<dsc reserve="673" >overrideQuote.origin = originQuote.origin

overrideQuote.ask = overrideQuote.bid+quotePolicyDetail.spreadPoints 
if(quotePolicyDetail.isOriginHiLo)
{
	overrideQuote.high = originQuote.high
	overrideQuote.low = originQuote.low
}
else
{
	if(!quotePolicyDetail.high || 
	overrideQuote.ask &gt; quotePolicyDetail.high)
		overrideQuote.high = overrideQuote.ask
	else
		overrideQuotation.high = quotePolicyDetail.high
	if(!quotePolicyDetail.low || 
	overrideQuote.bid &lt; quotePolicyDetail.low)
		overrideQuote.low = overrideQuote.bid
	else
		overrideQuote.low = quotePolicyDetail.low
}
